                     <interp inst="t18250915-31-off162" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250915-31-cd163" type="crimeDate">28th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-31-off162 t18250915-31-cd163"></join>, a watch, value 1 l., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-31-victim263" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Jones
                     <interp inst="t18250915-31-victim263" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
